But she's not dead.

1456
01:54:07,877 --> 01:54:10,628
我们找到了她,把她又放回去了.
We found her, restored her.

1457
01:54:10,838 --> 01:54:13,245
她还被冰冻着,还活着...
She's still frozen alive...

1458
01:54:13,466 --> 01:54:14,711
等你找到治疗方法.
...waiting for you to find a cure.

1459
01:54:14,926 --> 01:54:17,630
Huh? 她还活着?
She lives?

1460
01:54:17,846 --> 01:54:19,672
