So I'm asking you.

1466
01:54:40,619 --> 01:54:42,777
Victor Fries...
Victor Fries...

1467
01:54:42,996 --> 01:54:44,988
帮我拯救另一条生命.
...help me save another life.

1468
01:54:45,207 --> 01:54:47,958
告诉我如何治疗Macgregor综合症的第一阶段...
Show me how to cure Macgregor's Syndrome, stage one.

1469
01:54:48,168 --> 01:54:50,456
